OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with late sunshine, then long
OL,7,Fclear spells after sunset. Long clear
OL,8,Fspells overnight, but a few mist and
OL,9,Ffog patches possibly forming,
OL,10,Fespecially in the east. Perhaps a
OL,11,Ftouch of frost in rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FAny isolated mist and fog
OL,14,Fpatches will be quick clear leaving a
OL,15,Fdry day with light winds and
OL,16,Fpredominantly clear skies giving
OL,17,Fplenty of sunshine. Feeling warm in
OL,18,Fthe sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
